    if (!purchaseData.suppliers.length) { purchaseTab = "suppliers"; toast(l("Voeg eerst een leverancier toe", "Ajoutez d’abord un fournisseur", "Add a supplier first"), "info"); openSupplierEditor(); return; }
    const isEdit = Boolean(order); let lines = (order && order.lines && order.lines.length ? order.lines : [{ description: "", articleId: "", orderedQty: 1, unit: "st", unitPrice: 0, vatRate: 21 }]).map(row => ({ ...row }));
    const lineHtml = () => lines.map((line, index) => `<div class="pws-line" data-po-line="${index}"><label>${esc(l("Omschrijving", "Description", "Description"))}<input data-line-field="description" value="${esc(line.description || "")}"></label><label>${esc(l("Artikel", "Article", "Article"))}<select data-line-field="articleId">${optionRows(purchaseData.articles, line.articleId, row => `${row.number || ""} · ${row.name}`, l("Vrije lijn", "Ligne libre", "Free line"))}</select></label><label>${esc(l("Aantal", "Quantité", "Qty"))}<input data-line-field="orderedQty" type="number" min="0.01" step="0.01" value="${esc(line.orderedQty || 1)}"></label><label>${esc(l("Eenheid", "Unité", "Unit"))}<input data-line-field="unit" value="${esc(line.unit || "st")}"></label><label>${esc(l("Eenheidsprijs", "Prix unitaire", "Unit price"))}<input data-line-field="unitPrice" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="${esc(line.unitPrice || 0)}"></label><button type="button" data-line-remove="${index}" aria-label="${esc(l("Lijn verwijderen", "Supprimer la ligne", "Remove line"))}">×</button></div>`).join("");
    setEditor(isEdit ? l("Bestelling bewerken", "Modifier la commande", "Edit purchase order") : l("Nieuwe bestelling", "Nouvelle commande", "New purchase order"), l("Aankoopwerkruimte", "Espace achats", "Purchasing workspace"), `<form id="pwsPurchaseForm" class="pws-editor">${intro("PO", l("Bestelling opbouwen", "Composer la commande", "Build the purchase order"), l("Besteld, ontvangen en gefactureerd worden per lijn afzonderlijk opgevolgd.", "Commandé, reçu et facturé sont suivis séparément par ligne.", "Ordered, received and invoiced quantities are tracked separately per line."))}<div class="pws-form-grid"><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Leverancier", "Fournisseur", "Supplier"))}</label><select name="supplierId" required>${optionRows(purchaseData.suppliers, order && order.supplierId, row => row.name)}</select></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Type", "Type", "Type"))}</label><select name="type">${[["material", l("Materiaal", "Matériel", "Material")], ["subcontract", l("Onderaanneming", "Sous-traitance", "Subcontract")], ["rental", l("Huur", "Location", "Rental")], ["transport", "Transport"]].map(([value, label]) => `<option value="${value}" ${order && order.type === value ? "selected" : ""}>${esc(label)}</option>`).join("")}</select></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Project", "Projet", "Project"))}</label><select name="projectId">${optionRows(purchaseData.projects, order && order.projectId || projectPrefill, row => `${row.number || ""} · ${row.name}`, l("Geen project", "Aucun projet", "No project"))}</select></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Ontvangstlocatie", "Lieu de réception", "Receipt location"))}</label><select name="locationId">${optionRows(purchaseData.venues, order && order.locationId, row => row.name || row.address, l("Nog niet bepaald", "Pas encore défini", "Not set yet"))}</select></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Besteldatum", "Date de commande", "Order date"))}</label><input name="orderDate" type="date" required value="${esc(order && order.orderDate || today())}"></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Verwachte levering", "Livraison prévue", "Expected delivery"))}</label><input name="expectedDate" type="date" value="${esc(order && order.expectedDate || "")}"></div><div class="adm-form-group wide"><label>${esc(l("Leveradres", "Adresse de livraison", "Delivery address"))}</label><input name="deliveryAddress" value="${esc(order && order.deliveryAddress || "")}"></div></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Bestellijnen", "Lignes de commande", "Order lines"))}</label><div id="pwsPurchaseLines" class="pws-line-list">${lineHtml()}</div><button type="button" class="adm-btn adm-btn-secondary adm-btn-sm" id="pwsAddPurchaseLine">+ ${esc(l("Lijn toevoegen", "Ajouter une ligne", "Add line"))}</button></div><div class="adm-form-group"><label>${esc(l("Notities", "Notes", "Notes"))}</label><textarea name="notes">${esc(order && order.notes || "")}</textarea></div>${actionsRow()}</form>`, "product-wide");
    const form = document.getElementById("pwsPurchaseForm"); const lineHost = document.getElementById("pwsPurchaseLines"); bindCancel(form);
    const syncLines = () => { lineHost.querySelectorAll("[data-po-line]").forEach((row, index) => { row.querySelectorAll("[data-line-field]").forEach(input => { lines[index][input.dataset.lineField] = ["orderedQty", "unitPrice"].includes(input.dataset.lineField) ? Number(input.value) : input.value; }); }); };
    const redraw = () => { lineHost.innerHTML = lineHtml(); bindLines(); };
    const bindLines = () => { lineHost.querySelectorAll("[data-line-field]").forEach(input => input.addEventListener("input", syncLines)); lineHost.querySelectorAll("[data-line-remove]").forEach(button => button.addEventListener("click", () => { syncLines(); if (lines.length > 1) lines.splice(Number(button.dataset.lineRemove), 1); redraw(); })); };
